snippet.title: Ultra Mega Cats - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1882130/Ultra_Mega_Cats/

Blast your way through hordes of enemies in Ultra Mega Cats, a cooperative roguelike third-person shooter. As one of the Mega Cats, you’re armed to the fangs with a wide variety of abilities, and it’s your job to escape a corporate captivity, while freeing all three Ancient Cats in the process.
